modName: No ugly dead ivy in Windhelm
summary: Simply removes ugly 2d ivy from few Windhelm buildings.
descriptionHtml: Simply removes ugly 2d ivy from few Windhelm buildings. There is not much to say actually. Made this for personal use, but maybe someone else would like it. Absolutely safe as not edits any cells, not contains any scripts. There is no even esp actually. It just contains vanilla mesh with removed 2d ivy overlay.
author: mluppov
